{
  "stem": "23131.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For that, they gave us a piece of bread, they gave us some-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in the-- in the cans, used to come, you know, for the military people, always comes in cans, all kind of foods, which at that time, was already a little problem with food.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They used to pay us not in money, you understand, but in products, in food, mostly.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At night, we used-- we had-- we weren't restricted not to go out in this and this-- after this and this hour, like in the ghettos.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they used the come to a porch of my girlfriend's where we used to get together all, and sit with us and tell us jokes and-- and sing with us.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we thought they were our friends.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was later on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was later on, the yellow star.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, definitely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We weren't allow--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we weren't-- [INAUDIBLE] when it comes to business, this was immediately.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jews had no right to do anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we weren't restricted, you know, like in the ghetto, in a closed ghetto, not to go out, and--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We worked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we washed the floors.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We cleaned the-- their rooms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They decided.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They decided.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, the certain spot, which near my house was the spot where it was a whole unit of Germans that-- it was their station there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's-- it was easy to get there because it was even at a quarter of a block.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and they decided, you do this, you do this, you do this, you'll do that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We couldn't decide it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the beginning, I'm telling you, I didn't feel anything bad.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were very polite, they were very nice, and they didn't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
